item.title: Testing out
item.content:encoded:
This is my first heading on my first blog post

Using this publish to pages plugin in joplin seems like it could be a breeze. I can pump out some posts before I mess with the theme and get something rolling. Will it integrate well with jekyll? Can I get something nice for the dnd journals?

I have no idea but it s a start and I just want to get started. I wonder how linked images will look. Might need to change my cloud serbice to something other than… What am I currently using again? Dropbox?
